  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13055384/finland_lapland_levi_levitunturi-spa-hotel_exterior1.jpg" alt="herolapland" data-udi="umb://media/ffba827de10b4ced88c97cd051076b26" /></p>
<h4>The highlights of Lapland lodgings - Inghams top picks on where to stay</h4>
<p>Lapland holidays are the perfect winter get away - from a weeks <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">skiing in the arctic circle</a>, a chance to search for the <a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights">northern lights</a>, experience the culture through <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Excursions">husky sleigh rides and snowmobiles</a> or getting into the festive spirit and popping in to <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">greet Santa</a> before the big day. </p>
<p>A <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland holiday</a> is once in a lifetime experience and it can be hard to decide where you want to stay and the type of accommodation you want to stay in to ensure you have the ultimate Lapland holiday and soak in every moment you are there. </p>
<p>To help make the decision easier for you, we have hand-picked some of our top places to stay across our <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">3 resorts</a>. Whether you are after traditional, cosy cabins, home from home apartments or all the luxury of a hotel stay - we are sure we have the place to suit you. </p>
<h2>Log Cabins</h2>
<p>The moment you arrive, you will be enchanted by their charm - snowy roof tops, a warm window glow and surrounded by woodland. If you are hoping to immerse yourself in the <a data-udi="umb://document/b6809554a2464598a32339bf6fe5475d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b6809554a2464598a32339bf6fe5475d}" title="Lapland Fact File">Finnish way of life</a>, then a log cabin stay is the best way to do so.</p>
<p>Traditional on the outside, but with all the modern conveniences on the inside. Hidden amongst the trees so privacy is key but never too far from all the local amenities and restaurants, a cabin stay is the prefect retreat. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a64717f77a214ef9a7be6f05c4ca8e4f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a64717f77a214ef9a7be6f05c4ca8e4f}" title="Yllas Log Cabins">Ylläs Log Cabins</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13055797/finland_lapland_yllas_yllas_log_cabin_exterior2.jpg" alt="yllaslogcabin" data-udi="umb://media/bfaea99c0ba0424ca7756abb756c0f1a" /></p>
<p>1 and bedroom cabins, opt for resort based more remote - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a></p>
<p>These warming cabins all come with their own saunas and fireplaces.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c5c249c2b1fd449981854291fa2ae03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c249c2b1fd449981854291fa2ae03d}" title="Villa Armas Cabins">Villa Armas Cabins</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13055817/finland_lapland_yllas_villa_armas_cabins_exterior.jpg" alt="villaarmas" data-udi="umb://media/998d82bf166b4012afcc2d33cc74e5ef" /></p>
<p>2 bed cabins, close to the village centre and also the ski slopes - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a></p>
<p>In the perfect, Lappish location with an open fireplace and cosy décor.<a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas"></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/88ab24140f494052864fd3b80baa80e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/88ab24140f494052864fd3b80baa80e4}" title="Kuukkeli Log Cabins">Kuukkeli Log Cabins</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099806/saariselka-cabin-1.jpg" alt="saariselkacabin" data-udi="umb://media/25e2f3bd57944827b6dc2167605ea1c4" /></p>
<p>2 to 6 bed cabins, located in the centre of the resort and close to restaurants - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a></p>
<p>Traditional Lappish décor with a cosy feel and access to Saunas.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Apartments</h2>
<p>Apartments are the ideal place to stay if you want all the <a data-udi="umb://document/a834c4c53a594cb2b8d5c4a2ac436000" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a834c4c53a594cb2b8d5c4a2ac436000}" title="Lapland Folklore">tradition and feel of local Lapland</a>, but also want to make yourself at home for your holiday. The apartments are comfortable and spacious with fully equipped kitchens so you can go about your family routine, just with an extra special view.</p>
<p>Apartments in Lapland are still designed to fit in with their surroundings and therefore still provide that feeling of staying somewhere special and unique, perfect for matching your magical holiday experience overall. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8f553700b9f8447386f7cfd67ee9914e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8f553700b9f8447386f7cfd67ee9914e}" title="Levi Black Apartments">Levi Black Apartments</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13094659/exterior.jpg" alt="leviblack" data-udi="umb://media/c29c4ba8acd94674900428cf889ac6ea" /></p>
<p>6 to 8 bed apartment, great proximity to resort facilities including bus stops - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a></p>
<p>Central location apartments, across 2 floors with private sauna and access to whirlpools.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c5c249c2b1fd449981854291fa2ae03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c249c2b1fd449981854291fa2ae03d}" title="Villa Armas Cabins">Top Star Arctic Cubes</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13094151/cabin-and-northern-lights.jpg" alt="topstarcube" data-udi="umb://media/2cdfcff8483442f8804b1c5f9324c24d" /></p>
<p>2 to 4 bed apartments, in a quiet location with a bus to resort centre - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a></p>
<p>Panoramic window views, these apartments offer style and comfort with private sauna.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/bf468fcb126a4a26869b3a613337ba17" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bf468fcb126a4a26869b3a613337ba17}" title="Sirius and Orion Apartments">Sirius &amp; Orion Apartments</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13094445/apartment_building_exterior-1.jpg" alt="siriusorion" data-udi="umb://media/db4856b3fd1640689b707ed79a3727ef" /></p>
<p>2 to 6 bed apartments, perfect central location to resorts main street - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a></p>
<p>These are high standard and modern apartments with elegant touches of local design. </p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Hotels</h2>
<p>A hotel stay is the perfect option if you want to sit back, relax and and enjoy comfort and catering. Set in ideal locations across <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">resorts</a>, hotels provide the ease and convenience you hope for on holiday. With a mix of traditional and modern, hotels in Lapland provide a great setting for your winter escape. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec}" title="Levi Hotel Spa">Levi Hotel Spa</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13098978/levihotelspa-2.jpg" alt="hotelspa" data-udi="umb://media/a6c1340a2e4349ff970eaf86e462e068" /></p>
<p>Family and suite bedrooms, multiple on site facilities on the edge of town - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a></p>
<p>Situated in a peaceful yet easy location with a large spa area, it is a high-standard hotel with quality catering. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2}" title="Muotka Wilderness Lodge">Muotka wilderness</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13091659/moutka_wilderness_lodge_panorama_log_cabin_outside.jpg" alt="wildernesshotel" data-udi="umb://media/014dfa6674af4fa6b09a0a3e808ce7ee" /></p>
<p>Rooms, suites and cabins in its own mini-resort area offering a full winter itinerary - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a></p>
<p>Offering a range of facilities in a quiet setting, providing a true Lappish wonderland.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel">Saaga Spa hotel</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13080112/lapland-hotel-saaga-3.jpg" alt="saagaspa" data-udi="umb://media/843980670cef455d858f61a865ec3c89" /></p>
<p>Range of rooms options including single occupancy rated rooms, with a high-end on-site spa - Resort of: <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a></p>
<p>A very modern, luxury hotel with ski-in ski-out option. Everything you need is in this mini resort hotel.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Where to visit</h2>
<p>Still deciding what resort you would like to visit? have a look at our 3 resorts across Lapland and all the accommodation options at each destination. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13095227/inghams-lapland-5-billion-star-service.jpeg" alt="leviresort" data-udi="umb://media/3e6ff02a1615415f99b83c2687ae629b" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" class="c-btn">Levi</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13095245/inghams-lapland-finland-saariselka.jpeg" alt="yllasresort" data-udi="umb://media/e5325801d0794d42a6b4509640486f27" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" class="c-btn">Yllas</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13095242/inghams-lapland-adobestock_288733450.jpeg" alt="saariselkaresort" data-udi="umb://media/56d10193110847028f24ae22b433f4f5" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" class="c-btn">Saariselka</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
